Volkswagen Says It Will Invest More Than $86 Billion Over Next Five Years

-- B y   R a j i v   S e k h r i
-- 
2011-09-16T09:28:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/volkswagen-says-it-will-invest-more-than-86-billion-over-next-five-years.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW)  will invest more than
62 billion euros until 2016 on developing new models,
environmentally safe technologies and facilities, the company
said in an e-mailed statment today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
